[{"jobid":1,"active":true,"command":"SELECT public.refresh_all_rollups();","jobname":"rollups_refresh_every_15m","database":"postgres","nodename":"localhost","nodeport":5432,"schedule":"*/15 * * * *","username":"postgres"},{"jobid":3,"active":true,"command":"SELECT public.refresh_cost_analysis_mv();","jobname":"refresh_cost_analysis_mv_nightly","database":"postgres","nodename":"localhost","nodeport":5432,"schedule":"10 2 * * *","username":"postgres"},{"jobid":4,"active":true,"command":"
  UPDATE public.transactions t
  SET
    line_items_total = COALESCE(agg.total_amount, 0),
    line_items_count = COALESCE(agg.items_count, 0),
    has_line_items   = COALESCE(agg.items_count, 0) > 0,
    updated_at = NOW()
  FROM (
    SELECT
      li.transaction_id,
      COUNT(*) AS items_count,
      COALESCE(SUM(li.total_amount), 0) AS total_amount
    FROM public.transaction_line_items li
    GROUP BY li.transaction_id
  ) agg
  WHERE t.id = agg.transaction_id
     OR NOT EXISTS (
       SELECT 1 FROM public.transaction_line_items li WHERE li.transaction_id = t.id
     );
  ","jobname":"reconcile_transaction_snapshots_weekly","database":"postgres","nodename":"localhost","nodeport":5432,"schedule":"20 2 * * 0","username":"postgres"}]
